  <brief_title>A Multicenter Study to Evaluate the ROX Anastomotic Coupler System (ACS) In Patients With Severe Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Non-Randomized, Open Label, Multi-Center Study to Evaluate the ROX Anastomotic Coupler System (ACS) in Patients With Severe Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>ROX Medical, Inc.</agency>
