  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of severe hypertension must be made on the basis of current findings,
             medical history, and physical examination

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any serious medical condition that may adversely affect the patient's safety, limit
             the subject's ability to participate in the study, comply with follow-up requirements
             or impact the scientific integrity of the study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
